extendedInfo.description: Warning! Cuteness overload! Bunny Rabbit Live Wallpaper is in town and this cute bunny brings you joy. This is a free Android app with fantastic animated pictures of bunnies.Bunny Rabbit live wallpaper is fantastic for all the people who love cartoon bunnies, perfect for boys and girls but also for adults who would like to cheer up whenever they look at their phone. This is animal live wallpaper featuring extra fluffy bunny. Now your wallpapers and backgrounds can have soul and live up a bit! Personalize your home screen. This is a free-to-download app, and here you can find a lot of different pet live wallpapers. Choose one of the six cute bunny pictures, set it as live wallpaper and make your phone the cutest ever.  There are five kinds of bunnies that move their cute noses, dressed in fashionable bunny suits. Find your favorite one and then place it in the background you want and have fun with your new pet rabbit. These HD wallpapers are wallpapers for boys, but no one can tell that these are not wallpapers for girls.
